title: Group Therapy: The boss that doesn't know technology
description: Gianna calls in to ask for advice about a problem with her boss.  Her boss is a little older and asks for help with EVERYTHING technology-related.  She doesn't know how to attach something in an email, use Dropbox, the list goes on and she needs help on what to do.
